+dnl @synopsis MN_C_COMPILER_IS_CLANG
+dnl
+dnl Find out if a compiler claiming to be gcc really is gcc (fuck you clang).
+dnl @version 1.0	Oct 31 2013
+dnl @author Erik de Castro Lopo <erikd AT mega-nerd DOT com>
+dnl
